<item>
            <title>[LU-19212] enable quota enforcement via &apos;quota_slave*.enabled=ugp&apos; by default</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19212</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We repeatedly get questions/issues raised because quota enforcement is not enabled in Lustre by default.  It would be better to enable &quot;&lt;tt&gt;ugp&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; quota enforcement by default instead of &quot;&lt;tt&gt;none&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;, and if something else is set in the configuration (e.g. &quot;&lt;tt&gt;ug&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;) then this would override the default value.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
